Freeway: Interstate Highway or other [[State highway|state]] or [[United States Numbered Highways|U.S. Route]] built to Interstate standards.

'''[[Divided highway|Divided rural]]''': State or U.S. route, generally with four or more lanes, not built to Interstate standards, but with a median or other divider separating directions of travel.

'''Undivided rural''': [[County highway|County]], State, or U.S. route, generally with two to four lanes, with no separator between directions of travel.

'''Residential Street/residential''': Residential streets, business districts, or [[School zones]].
